text: Paulin Obame-Nguema (28 December 1934. - 11 December 2023) was a Gabonese politician. He was the Prime Minister of Gabon from 2 November 1994 to 23 January 1999. He was a Deputy in the National Assembly of Gabon. Obame-Nguema died on 11 December 2023 at the age of 88.Disparition : Paulin Obame Nguéma, ce Premier ministre tout en humilité ==References== Category:1934 births Category:2023 deaths Category:Prime Ministers of Gabon
